  "texts": [
    "• WuDaoCorpora-Text (Yuan et al, 2021).",
    "The WuDaoCorpora-Text corpus has a pure text size of approximately 5TB, comprising over 50 industry data labels such as education and technology.",
    "The corpus has crawled a rich set of Chinese webpage data.",
    "Currently, 200GB of texts have been released as open source.",
    "A.1.2 Languages Texts • ANC 67."
